  <L=26#7> Folder </L> Folder ( <L=51#6> String </L> path )

Parameters 

  --------- ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  path      The absolute or relative path to the folder associated with this object, specified in URI
            format.

  --------- ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Creates and returns a new Folder object referring to a given file-system location.

If the path name refers to an already existing disk file, a File object is returned instead. Returns the
new Folder object.

