Object.toSource 

  <L=51#6> String </L> toSource ()

Description 

Creates and returns a string representation of this object.

This function serializes the object, so that it can, for example, be passed between engines. Pass the
returned string back to?eval()?to recreate the object. Works only with built-in classes.

