Socket.listen 

  bool listen ( <L=3r#5> Number </L> port , <L=51#6> String </L> encoding )

Parameters 

  ------------------------ -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  port                     The TCP/IP port number to listen on.

  encoding                 The encoding to be used for the connection
  ------------------------ -------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Instructs the object to start listening for an incoming connection.

The call to open() and the call to listen()are mutually exclusive. Call one function or the other, not
both.

