Socket.read 

  <L=51#6> String </L> read ( <L=3r#5> Number </L> count )

Parameters 

  ------------------------ -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  count                    The number of characters to read.

  ------------------------ -------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description 

Reads up to the specified number of characters from the connection. CR characters are ignored unless the
encoding is set to “BINARY”.

Returns a string that contains up to the number of characters that were supposed to be read, or the
number of characters read before the connection closed or timed out.

