XML.hasComplexContent 

  bool hasComplexContent ()

Description 

Reports whether this XML object contains complex content.

An XML object is considered to contain complex content if it represents an XML element that has child
elements. XML objects representing attributes, comments, processing instructions and text nodes do not
have complex content. The existence of attributes, comments, processing instructions and text nodes
within an XML object is not significant in determining if it has complex content.

<I=2>
</B>
=========================================================================================================
